Package: treestructure
Type: Package
Title: Detect Population Structure Within Phylogenetic Trees
Version: 0.0.2
Date: 2019-11-02
Author: Erik Volz
Maintainer: Erik Volz <erik.volz@gmail.com>
Description: This package implements algorithms for detecting population structure from the history of coalescent events recorded in phylogenetic trees. The *trestruct* method classifies each tip and internal node of a tree into disjoint sets characterized by similar coalescent patterns. 
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: ape
Suggests: ggtree 
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.19)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
